      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with plenty of character? This vehicle is ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a solid, functional car at a great price. It's the perfect opportunity to own a quality vehicle that\u2019s ready to go while leaving room for a little personal touch-up!",
