      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This model has been curated to meet rigorous standards, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust mechanical profile, it represents a superior acquisition for the discerning driver who values integrity and enduring style. We invite you to experience its refined road manners firsthand.",
