    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65B40 naturally aspirated V8 era. Delivering 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline, the powerplant is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for precision corner exit. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC coated shells and ARP bolts, and the throttle actuators have been upgraded. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains stiff, providing the communicative feedback expected of the M-division's engineering. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its history, the drivetrain and subframe mounting points are in excellent order, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 31850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Engine runs smooth. Clean interior. Reliable daily driver. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 32000.0,
