    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior finish still holds a deep, impressive gloss, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful use such as tiny stone chips on the front valence. All original alloy wheels are free of major curbing and are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, while the dashboard and trim pieces show no sun fading or cracking. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the high-fidelity infotainment system, is in full working order. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, evidenced by a thick folder of service receipts. The engine is quiet and responsive, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. This is a turn-key vehicle that has been loved by its previous owner and is ready for many more miles of reliable service. Includes two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
